<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>数学作业系统 - 明舟教育</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei",sans-serif;}
        body{background:#fff3e0;max-width:700px;margin:50px auto;padding:20px;}
        .title{text-align:center;color:#ff9800;margin-bottom:40px;font-size:28px;}
        .enter-box{display:flex;gap:20px;}
        .enter-card{flex:1;background:white;padding:40px 20px;border-radius:16px;text-align:center;}
        .enter-btn{padding:12px 25px;border:none;border-radius:8px;cursor:pointer;margin-top:15px;}
        .student-btn{background:#07c160;color:white;}
        .teacher-btn{background:#2b85ff;color:white;}
        .back-home{text-align:center;margin-top:30px;}
        .back-home button{padding:10px 20px;background:#666;color:white;border:none;cursor:pointer;}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<h1 class="title">➡️ 数学作业系统</h1>
<div class="enter-box">
    <div class="enter-card">
        <div style="font-size:40px;">👨‍🎓</div>
        <h3>学生端</h3>
        <p>查看作业、提交作业、看讲解</p>
        <button class="enter-btn student-btn" onclick="location.href='student-homework.html'">学生进入</button>
    </div>
    <div class="enter-card">
        <div style="font-size:40px;">👨‍🏫</div>
        <h3>教师端</h3>
        <p>布置作业、传视频、查提交</p>
        <button class="enter-btn teacher-btn" onclick="location.href='homework-module.html'">教师进入</button>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="back-home">
    <button onclick="location.href='index.html'">← 返回校区官网</button>
</div>
</body>
</html>
